Given the explicit merger stated in the resolution, I have a high degree of confidence in this result. Therefore, "Phường 14, Quận 6, Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh" has been merged to become part of **Phường Phú Lâm**. The confidence is high as this is explicitly stated.
